### ============================================
### Authentication Module
### ============================================
### Scalar Docs: {{baseUrl}}/scalar/v1
### Demo Users:
###   - admin@demo.corelio.app / Admin123!
###   - manager@demo.corelio.app / Admin123!
###   - cashier@demo.corelio.app / Admin123!

@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001

### Login with Admin user
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@demo.corelio.app",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

###

### Login with Manager user
# @name loginManager
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "manager@demo.corelio.app",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

###

### Login with Cashier user
# @name loginCashier
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "cashier@demo.corelio.app",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

###

### Refresh access token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{loginAdmin.response.body.refreshToken}}"
}

###

### Logout (Revoke refresh token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{loginAdmin.response.body.refreshToken}}"
}

###

### Request password reset
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@demo.corelio.app"
}
